ZH: 我们的住所离学校有五公里远。
EN: Our house is five kilometers away from the school.

ZH: 他每天骑自行车去公司，来回大约要三十公里。
EN: He rides his bicycle to work every day, which is about thirty kilometers round trip.

ZH: 我们的目的地离这里只有十公里。
EN: Our destination is only ten kilometers from here.

ZH: 这段路程大约有二百公里。
EN: This journey is about two hundred kilometers.

ZH: 火车每小时可以跑五百公里。
EN: The train can run five hundred kilometers per hour.

ZH: 我们今天要开车去郊外，在高速公路上行驶将近六十公里。
EN: We are driving to the outskirts today, traveling nearly sixty kilometers on the highway.

ZH: 这个村庄离城市非常远，大约有四十公里。
EN: This village is very far from the city, about forty kilometers away.

ZH: 这个景点到我们的酒店只有两公里。
EN: The scenic spot is only two kilometers from our hotel.

ZH: 这座山的最高峰海拔两千米。
EN: The highest peak of this mountain is two kilometers above sea level.

ZH: 我们计划在周末骑自行车到海边，大约有一百公里的距离。
EN: We plan to bike to the beach over the weekend, a distance of about one hundred kilometers.

ZH: 这架飞机每小时飞行八百公里。
EN: This airplane flies at a speed of eight hundred kilometers per hour.

ZH: 我们昨天爬了四公里高的山。
EN: We climbed a four-kilometer-high mountain yesterday.

ZH: 这个城市每年举办一次马拉松比赛，总长约四十二公里。
EN: This city holds a marathon once a year, with a total distance of about forty-two kilometers.

ZH: 我每晚步行回家，距离车站有两公里。
EN: I walk home every night, two kilometers from the train station.

ZH: 那座桥长一公里。
EN: That bridge is one kilometer long.

ZH: 他跑步训练每天都要跑五公里。
EN: He runs five kilometers for training every day.

ZH: 今天的徒步路线总长约六十公里。
EN: Today's hiking route is about sixty kilometers in total.

ZH: 这座湖面积达一百平方公里。
EN: This lake has an area of one hundred square kilometers.

ZH: 这个国家的面积是十万平方公里。
EN: The area of this country is one hundred thousand square kilometers.

ZH: 这里的海滩沿线有三公里长。
EN: The beach here is three kilometers long.
